Uses of Interface
edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter.IInterpreter

  • Packages that use IInterpreter 
    Package Description
    edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter
    The Interpreter package provides support for transformational interpretation of a source programming language.
    edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.parser
    The Parser package defines an abstract parser used by the transformational interpreter, and a generic end-of-statement detector.
    edu.uidaho.junicon.substrates.junicon
    Contains the customized Junicon interpreter.

      Classes in edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter that implement IInterpreter 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  AbstractShell
      Base implementation of a transformational multi-interpreter used by both the command shell, or meta-interpreter, and sub-interpreters for specific languages.
      class  CommandShell
      CommandShell is an outer interpretive shell implemented using a transformational meta-interpreter.
      class  TransformInterpreter
      TransformInterpreter implements a base transformational interpreter that performs multi-stage transforms on its input and then executes the result on a script engine substrate.
